A supplementary Machine Learning and Evolutionary Computation suite for Orange. It provides a set of tools for Machine Learning (ML) and Evoluationary Computation (EC) such as:
  • Optimization Meta-heuristics (EDAs, cGA)
  • Feature Selection
  • Kernel Methods
  • Dependency Networks

Qt is a cross-platform application and UI framework for developers using C++ or QML, a CSS & JavaScript like language. Qt Creator is the supporting Qt IDE.
QT is used by Orange and the Goldenberry components to provide a GUI so that the user can wire and execute them from a friendly user interface.
For more infromation go to http://qt-project.org
